| `/api/creator/generate-content` (titles) | Title Generation | `lib/gemini-service.js` | 0.7 |
| `/api/creator/generate-content` (hashtags) | Hashtag Generation | `lib/gemini-service.js` | 0.7 |
| `/api/creator/ideas` | Content Ideas | `lib/gemini-service.js` | 0.8 |
| `/api/creator/analyze-niche-content` | Niche Analysis | `app/api/creator/analyze-niche-content/route.js` | 0.7 |
| `/api/ai/generate-reply` | Comment Reply | `lib/gemini.js` | 0.8 |

